<li>deviation of angle of mouth, drooling of saliva VII</li>
<li>loss of taste sensation </li>
<li>vertigo, tinnitus, deafness VIII</li>
<li>nasal regurgitation &amp; twang IX,X</li>
<li>recurrent choking episodes ,hoarseness of voice X</li>
<li>dysphagia “</li>
<li>drooping of shoulders</li>
<li>wasting of tongue, dysarthria XII</li>
